@node Main "Eqwi - Documentation"

                               'Eqwi' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Eqwi' is a Workbench @{" game " link play} where you try to remove all tiles
from a game board. To do this, you have to place tiles so that 3
tiles of the same type are following each other in a 'corridor'. To
complete a game board, you have to eliminate all tiles from one
corridor, including the tile located in the center of the game
board, which is indicated by a 'pressed down' space. When one
corridor is emptied, the remaining tiles from the other corridor
are eliminated and the game continues... unless one corridor is
completely filled up, in that case the game will be over.

  Have fun!

               @{" Install and Play the game " link play}
